::he hears Motormaster::
Cyclonus: Good to hear your voice again Motormaster. What do you want me to 
do?
~~~~~
Time Warp: Judging from whats going on at that battle Prowl and iron raptor 
are going to kill each other. What are you going to do? Well, we gotta keep 
searching. Maybe we'll find her someday. But till then, we need someplace to 
take shelter, dont you think?
